Day 4 marked the culmination of our karting odyssey – a testament to resilience, teamwork, and unyielding determination! Despite encountering technical hurdles along the way, our team stood strong, facing each challenge with unwavering resolve. Enduring on the race track was not just a victory, but a proud moment for every member who poured their heart and soul into this journey. Today, victory wasn't just about crossing the finish line; it was about celebrating every obstacle overcome and every moment of triumph. And amidst the intensity of the race, our team member Vrusti Gala stood out, earning a special mention as the Best Female Participant in the EV category. Though the road was not without its bumps, we emerged stronger, more united than ever before. As we reflect on our performance, we know that this is just the beginning. With lessons learned and spirits high, we're ready to rise from the setbacks and return even stronger. The race isn't over; it's only just begun. 🏁💪 #KartingEndurance #TeamResilience #RiseAndRace"
